snippet.title: Galves Adventure game walkthrough
snippet.description:
Ok, this is the solution of Galves Adventure from eyemaze site. You can play it in this site : http://www.kotarogame.com/archives/53702998.html ...

This is the evil solution, theres the good side too but I wont record it. The only thing I can tell you is that you have to take the golden orb instead of the dark one, duh! :P

Have fun and enjoy.
